name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: fs.s3a.connection.establish.timeout
description: Socket connection setup timeout in milliseconds.

name: dfs.replication
description:
Default block replication. 
  The actual number of replications can be specified when the file is created.
  The default is used if replication is not specified in create time.

name: dfs.namenode.metrics.logger.period.seconds
description:
This setting controls how frequently the NameNode logs its metrics. The
    logging configuration must also define one or more appenders for
    NameNodeMetricsLog for the metrics to be logged.
    NameNode metrics logging is disabled if this value is set to zero or
    less than zero.

name: dfs.qjournal.parallel-read.num-threads
description: Number of threads per JN to be used for tailing edits.

name: mapreduce.jobhistory.intermediate-user-done-dir.permissions
description:
The permissions of the user directories in
  ${mapreduce.jobhistory.intermediate-done-dir}. The user and the group
  permission must be 7, this is enforced.

name: dfs.namenode.decommission.blocks.per.interval
description:
The approximate number of blocks to process per decommission
    or maintenance interval, as defined in dfs.namenode.decommission.interval.
